{
    "text": "Love this hidden fairytale village in London. Did you know about it?  Warning:  Holly Village is private property. It looks incredible from the outside and you can see through the gates. So still worth going to admire the architecture. I was lucky and got chatting to a resident who let me take a closer look.  \ud83d\udccd Holly Village, Swain\u2019s Lane, Highgate  __________  #thecuriouspixiewanders #hollyvillage #highgate #highgatevillage #london #londonreels #visitlondon #explorelondon #discoverlondon #londonguide #thingstodoinlondon #londonlife #placestovisit #travel #traveltips #londontips #travelreels #londonblogger #travelblogger #uktravelblogger #beautifulbuildings #architecturelovers #archilovers",
